name: R5_v3_CodeSystem_for_R4B
title: Cross-version VS for R5.CodeSystem for use in FHIR R4B
description: This cross-version ValueSet represents concepts from http://terminology.hl7.org/ValueSet/v3-CodeSystem|2.0.0 for use in FHIR R4B. Concepts not present here have direct `equivalent` mappings crossing all versions from R5 to R4B.
